His Dad calls once every two weeks or so randomly, but makes the conversation about us, gets mad at my lack of response, and tells our son to just call him back later...and then he doesn't answer. I fear this is going to be the norm and I'm worried about the mental and emotional impact it will have on my son. I want him to know his Dad loves him, but I don't want him to be constantly wondering of he's going to be there for him or not.
